summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the improvement of the alley in Block 82, plat of Central Seattle (commonly known as McNaught's plat of Central Seattle), in Block 10, Walker's Addition, and between Lots 19 and 20 "McNaught's supplemental plat to Central Seattle", being a continuous alley between 18th Avenue South and 19th Avenue South and South Bayview Street to South College Street; by paving, etc.
